{"tid":1098443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌邨男子墮樓　當場身亡","createTime":"2019-04-09T05:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T07:03:09.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ba991d2b5b48e17a1d6cec8d8d55ec2ee774921","tid":1098443,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"葵涌有男子墮樓。今午(9日)12時，一名男子被發現自葵涌邨逸葵樓墮下，倒臥大廈對開行人路，重創昏迷，巨響驚動途人報警。救援人員趕至現場，證實年約60歲男子明顯死亡，警方封鎖現場，正調查死者身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=f35fd87d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190409/mobile/bkn-20190409122905541-0409_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190409%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190409122905541-0409_00822_001.html&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=6670672e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190409/mobile/bkn-20190409122905541-0409_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d7f1009b245d4787cedc75e58419460591b824d1","tid":1098443,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"個到係咪一年一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70dc5277a8864c3cdf63210b0a272e054f489d94","tid":1098443,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"葵涌邨幾乎隔幾個月跳一件"},{"pid":"34190db564df9be3aa313c292aa4cbc52f3715f0","tid":1098443,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70dc5277a8864c3cdf63210b0a272e054f489d94","t